<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>NVR on HelloWood</title><link>https://blog.hellowood.dev/tags/nvr/</link><description>Recent content in NVR on HelloWood</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>cn</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://blog.hellowood.dev/tags/nvr/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Frigate 使用 Hailo 8 或 Hailo 8L 进行对象识别</title><link>https://blog.hellowood.dev/posts/frigate-%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-hailo-8-%E6%88%96-hailo-8l-%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1%E8%AF%86%E5%88%AB/</link><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 11:25:24 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://blog.hellowood.dev/posts/frigate-%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-hailo-8-%E6%88%96-hailo-8l-%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1%E8%AF%86%E5%88%AB/</guid><description>&lt;p>Hailo8/Hailo-8L 是一家以色列的边缘人工智能公司发布的边缘加速器，定位和 &lt;a href="https://coral.ai/products/">Google Coral TPU&lt;/a> 完全一致；Hailo-8 算力为 26 TOPS，Hailo-8L 算力为 13 TOPS&lt;/p>
